# Implement workspace volume mounting logic

Implement the common workspace volume that all agents in a workspace share.

## Requirements

- Mount workspace root at `/workspace` in container
- Read-write access by default
- Workspace path from workspace record
- Validate workspace path exists and is accessible

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Workspace volume mounts to `/workspace` in container
- [ ] `get_workspace_path/1` retrieves workspace root from workspace_id
- [ ] Validates workspace directory exists
- [ ] Mount format compatible with Docker.ex `:volumes` option
- [ ] Support read-only mode via configuration
- [ ] Unit tests for workspace mount computation
